<=\n/section>=0A=0A=0A=0A\t<section class=3D\"generic\">=0A\t\t<hgroup><h1>Appetizin=\ng careers begin here</h1></hgroup>=0A\t\t<div>=0A\t\t\t<p>CPK is a great place t=\no start or enhance your restaurant career with flexible full - or part-time=\n work. People are our number one priority, and we're always looking for out=\nstanding hospitality-minded individuals to join our team at a place where w=\ne encourage you to be yourself. If you're ambitious and motivated, you'll l=\nove our energetic environment and dynamic company culture.</p>=0A\t\t</div>=\n=0A\t\t<aside class=3D\"expand-panels\">=0A\t\t\t<hgroup>=0A\t\t\t\t<h2>=0A\t\t\t\t\t<span>=\nExplore</span>=0A\t\t\t\t\t<span>Opportunities</span>=0A\t\t\t\t</h2>=0A\t\t\t</hgroup>=\n=0A\t\t\t<ul>=0A\t\t\t\t<li><a href=3D\"/careers/apply/\">Hourly</a></li>=0A\t\t\t\t<li>=\n<a href=3D\"http://tbe.taleo.net/NA4/ats/careers/jobSearch.jsp?org=3DCPK&cws=\n=3D1\">Management</a></li>=0A\t\t\t\t<li><a href=3D\"http://tbe.taleo.net/NA4/ats=\n/careers/searchResults.jsp?org=3DCPK&cws=3D2\">Restaurant Support Center</a>=\n</li>=0A\t\t\t</ul>=0A\t\t</aside>=0A\t</section>=0A\t=0A\t<section class=3D\"tabs c=\nlearfix tabs-generic positions\">=0A\t\t<div class=3D\"header\">=0A\t\t\t<hgroup><h=\n1>Choose an Exciting Career</h1></hgroup>=0A\t\t\t<p>Each restaurant offers th=\ne following positions</p>=0A\t\t\t<a href=3D\"/careers/apply/\" class=3D\"button =\napply-now\"><span>Apply Now</span></a>=0A\t\t</div>=0A\t\t<div class=3D\"tab firs=\nt\">=0A\t\t\t<hgroup><h2>Cook</h2></hgroup>=0A\t\t\t<div class=3D\"hidden\">=0A\t\t\t\t<=\np>If you have a passion for food and love preparing exciting cuisine, then =\nbecoming a member of our line cook team is a unique, fulfilling and gratify=\ning experience. Our Back of House staff is thoroughly trained in how to pre=\npare CPK's amazing dishes with consistency and accuracy, all in a great wor=\nk environment.</p>=0A\t\t\t\t<div class=3D\"img\" style=3D\"background-image:url(h=\nttp://info.cpk.com/cmspages/careers/cook_company.jpg);\"></div>=0A\t\t\t</div>=\n=0A\t\t</div>=0A\t\t<div class=3D\"tab\">=0A\t\t\t<hgroup><h2>Server</h2></hgroup>=\n=0A\t\t\t<div class=3D\"hidden\">=0A\t\t\t\t<p>Servers are the tour guides for the a=\ndventure of dining at CPK. Each time a guest visits our restaurants our ser=\nvers are given the opportunity to take them on a tour of the senses and hel=\np them discover all that CPK offers. A passion to please and strong custome=\nr service skills are a perfect fit for this position.</p>=0A\t\t\t\t<div class=\n=3D\"img\" style=3D\"background-image:url(http://info.cpk.com/cmspages/careers=\n/server_company.jpg);\"></div>=0A\t\t\t</div>=0A\t\t</div>=0A\t\t<div class=3D\"tab\">=\n=0A\t\t\t<hgroup><h2>Busser</h2></hgroup>=0A\t\t\t<div class=3D\"hidden\">=0A\t\t\t\t<p=\n>At CPK we know that our bussers act as the backbone of our operation. This=\n position is directly responsible for the flow of our restaurant, seating t=\nimes of guests and cleanliness. This role is not only challenging and fast =\npaced but rewarding and high energy.</p>=0A\t\t\t\t<div class=3D\"img\" style=3D\"=\nbackground-image:url(http://info.cpk.com/cmspages/careers/busser_company.jp=\ng);\"></div>=0A\t\t\t</div>=0A\t\t</div>=0A\t\t<div class=3D\"tab\">=0A\t\t\t<hgroup><h2=\n>Host/Hostess</h2></hgroup>=0A\t\t\t<div class=3D\"hidden\">=0A\t\t\t\t<p>Hosts and =\nHostesses play a vital role in the experience of our guests, providing the =\nfirst and last impression of the restaurant. In addition, the flow of the r=\nestaurant is controlled by guest seating. Be prepared to set the tone for t=\nhe restaurant and reflect the positive personality of CPK.</p>=0A\t\t\t\t<div c=\nlass=3D\"img\" style=3D\"background-image:url(http://info.cpk.com/cmspages/car=\neers/hostess_company.jpg);\"></div>=0A\t\t\t</div>=0A\t\t</div>=0A\t\t<div class=3D=\n\"tab\">=0A\t\t\t<hgroup class=3D\"small\"><h2>Counter/Take out<br> &amp; Bar</h2>=\n</hgroup>=0A\t\t\t<div class=3D\"hidden\">=0A\t\t\t\t<p>One of the highlights of CPK=\n's layout is our counter and bar that overlook the display kitchen. As gues=\nts enjoy their own live kitchen performance our Bar and Counter servers pro=\nvide them with amazing service, fantastic cocktails and inspiration for the=\nir order selection.</p>=0A\t\t\t\t<div class=3D\"img\" style=3D\"background-image:=\nurl(http://info.cpk.com/cmspages/careers/takeout_company.jpg);\"></div>=0A\t\t=\n\t</div>=0A\t\t</div>=0A\t\t=0A\t\t<div class=3D\"panel-display clearfix\">=0A\t\t\t<di=\nv class=3D\"details\"><div></div></div>=0A\t\t</div>=0A\t</section>=0A\t<section =\nclass=3D\"tabs clearfix tabs-generic steps\">=0A\t\t<div class=3D\"header\">=0A\t\t=\n\t<hgroup><h1>3 Steps to Success</h1></hgroup>=0A\t\t\t<p>We want you to grow w=\nith us and continue a successful career. Many of our long-standing, success=\nful team members started in entry level opportunities within operations. He=\nre's how we get our members on the path to success.</p>=0A\t\t</div>=0A\t\t<div=\n class=3D\"tab first step1\">=0A\t\t\t<hgroup><h2>Certified Trainer</h2></hgroup>=\n=0A\t\t\t<div class=3D\"hidden\">=0A\t\t\t\t<p>Certified trainers are responsible fo=\nr training all new hires at their restaurant and for assisting the managers=\n in maintaining CPK's high standards. You will become involved in managemen=\nt meetings, assist with special projects and be given the chance to partici=\npate in new store openings around the country (when available).</p>=0A\t\t\t\t<=\ndiv class=3D\"img\" style=3D\"background-image:url(http://info.cpk.com/cmspage=\ns/careers/trainer_hours_success.jpg);\"></div>=0A\t\t\t</div>=0A\t\t</div>=0A\t\t<d=\niv class=3D\"tab step2\">=0A\t\t\t<hgroup><h2>Shift Leader</h2></hgroup>=0A\t\t\t<d=\niv class=3D\"hidden\">=0A\t\t\t\t<p>Once you have completed the Certified Trainer=\n program, you will be eligible for promotion to either a Dining Room Shift =\nLeader (DSL) or Kitchen Shift Leader (KSL). At CPK, we believe that trainin=\ng is one of the keys to building a successful career. Our Shift Leader prog=\nrams are one of the best career development tools for team members interest=\ned in furthering their career in the restaurant industry. The programs offe=\nr in-depth knowledge through each area of management and have been designed=\n to prepare employees for the next level of responsibility. Training for bo=\nth programs include interactive workbooks, hands-on learning and curriculum=\n testing.</p>=0A\t\t\t\t<div class=3D\"img\" style=3D\"background-image:url(http:/=\n/info.cpk.com/cmspages/careers/shiftleader_hours_success.jpg);\"></div>=0A\t\t=\n\t</div>=0A\t\t</div>=0A\t\t<div class=3D\"tab step3\">=0A\t\t\t<hgroup><h2>Managemen=\nt</h2></hgroup>=0A\t\t\t<div class=3D\"hidden\">=0A\t\t\t\t<p>As California Pizza Ki=\ntchen continues to grow we will continue to promote from within. you.</p>  =0A          =0A        =0A          =0A=0A          =\n=0A            =0A            =0A                =0A                    =0A=\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=3D'row required full'>=0A\t     =0A\t                        <span>=0A\t                        \t<l=\nabel for=3D\"id_question\">Question</label>=0A\t                        </span>=\n=0A\t                        <textarea   =0A      =\n      =0A          =0A        =0A    </fieldset>  =0A  =0A=0A<input type=3D=\n\"submit\" value=3D\"Submit Inquiry\" class=3D\"submitInquiry\" />=0A=0A\t\t\t\t\t<a h=\nref=3D\"#\" class=3D\"hide-panel\">Hide Panel</a>=0A\t\t\t\t</div>=0A\t\t\t</form>    =\n        =0A\t\t=0A\t\t=0A\t\t<ol>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">What se=\nts CPK apart as a hospitality industry employer?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>Our people=\n, our&nbsp;<a href=3D\"http://www.cpk.com/faqs/careers/#rock\">R.O.C.K. philo=\nsophy</a>, our&nbsp;<a href=3D\"http://www.cpk.com/faqs/careers/#fourkeys\">F=\nour Keys to Success</a>&nbsp;and of course our unique&nbsp;<a href=3D\"http:=\n//www.cpk.com/menu/\">menu</a>. At CPK, we create an environment that inspir=\nes and challenges ambitious, motivated people to be themselves and be part =\nof a team working toward a common goal.</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t=\n\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">What is R.O.C.K.?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>CPK's R.O.C.K. philos=\nophy is our foundation. It stands for Respect, Opportunity, Communication a=\nnd Kindness. You can learn more about it on our&nbsp;<a href=3D\"http://www.=\ncpk.com/careers/inside-look/\">Inside CPK</a>&nbsp;page. We look to hire ind=\nividuals who embody these values to collaborate as a team, and help us to d=\neliver the very best CPK experience.</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<=\nspan class=3D\"q\">What are CPK&#39;s Four Keys to Success?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>C=\nPK has defined the four keys to our success as follows.</p>=0D=0A<ul>=0D=0A=\n<li>The First Key is our employees: we make CPK a great place to work.</li>=\n=0D=0A<li>The Second Key is our guests: we strive to amaze every guest ever=\ny time.</li>=0D=0A<li>The Third Key is our focus on sales and profit growth=\n: it's important for everyone to achieve financial success.</li>=0D=0A<li>T=\nhe Fourth Key is community: we are deeply committed to supporting our&nbsp;=\n<a href=3D\"http://www.cpk.com/company/community-relations/\">local communiti=\nes</a>.</li>=0D=0A</ul>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">=\nWhat opportunities are there for me to grow professionally at CPK?</span>=\n=0A\t\t\t\t<p>There are so many opportunities for growth at CPK. Check out our&=\nnbsp;<a href=3D\"http://www.cpk.com/careers/inside-look/\">Inside Look video<=\n/a>&nbsp;to see some of our success stories. Promotions are performance bas=\ned, which means your passion and dedication determine your growth. If you'r=\ne committed to your training and ongoing development, the sky's the limit.&=\nnbsp;</p>=0D=0A<p>Our goal is to promote 30% of our managers internally fro=\nm our hourly employees. Our most successful managers take an active role in=\n their development by asking questions, being inquisitive, taking initiativ=\ne and truly embracing the kitchen. To support your development, we provide =\na Career Path, as well as the mentorship of Senior General Managers and Sen=\nior Kitchen Managers.</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q=\n\">What type of management training and development program do you have at C=\nPK?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>CPK offers a 10-week comprehensive Management Training =\nProgram. The first 8 weeks are completed at a Certified Training Store (usu=\nally within the Region for which you&rsquo;ve been hired), during which you=\n are fully trained and certified in all Front of House and Back of House ho=\nurly positions. You also learn our menu, line checks, food ordering and rec=\neiving, opening and closing procedures and other management responsibilitie=\ns.&nbsp;</p>=0D=0A<p>Your final 2 weeks of training are completed at your h=\nome store to give you the opportunity to meet your staff, get acquainted wi=\nth your guests, become familiar with your store and set you up for success =\nin your position with your management team.</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=\n=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">What type of ongoing career development do you off=\ner?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>When you complete your training, you'll be ready to par=\nticipate in a variety of development opportunities. In addition to CPK Lead=\nership Workshops, we offer Management Decathlons, a 10-event skills challen=\nge hosted by Regional Directors and Trainers that combines fun and professi=\nonal development.&nbsp;</p>=0D=0A<p>The Regional Training Manager Program l=\nets managers within our stores become coaches and mentors to increase train=\ning and development within each region. CPK will also provide you with a Ca=\nreer Path and guide you towards your desired position. You'll also work wit=\nh mentors at various levels who will help keep your career moving forward.&=\nnbsp;CPK takes pride in promoting all of our General Managers from within i=\nn order to maintain a strong company culture. We believe the best way for C=\nPK to grow is to help our managers grow professionally and personally.</p>=\n=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">How is management struc=\ntured at CPK?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>We typically hire at either the Front of Hous=\ne (FOH) or Back of House (BOH) Manager level. All management promotions are=\n based upon performance in the restaurant. We usually run our restaurants w=\nith 3-5 managers per location, depending on the location's sales volume. Th=\ne management teams consist of multiple levels: FOH Manager, BOH Manager, As=\nsistant General Manager, Kitchen Manager and General Manager. We also have =\na Senior General Manager and Senior Kitchen Manager level for top performer=\ns who are developed into regional mentors.</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=\n=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">What type of benefits do you offer?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<=\np>Taking good care of our employees is simply part of our recipe for succes=\ns. We offer a highly achievable bonus program, potential six-figure compens=\nation for Senior General Managers, outstanding 401(k) with company match an=\nd medical benefits including Health, Dental and Vision coverage.</p>=0A\t\t\t<=\n/li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">How do I apply?</span>=0A\t\t\t\tY=\nou can&nbsp;<a href=3D\"http://www.cpk.com/careers/apply/\">apply online</a>.=\n<br />=0D=0AHourly applicants:=0D=0A<ul>=0D=0A<li>Online applications go di=\nrectly to the store.</li>=0D=0A<li>Most stores host weekly group interviews=\n so it would be beneficial to apply in person and ask if and when they are =\nhosting group interviews.</li>=0D=0A<li>All stores do hourly hiring individ=\nually. If there are multiple stores within your area, we recommend applying=\n at all locations individually</li>=0D=0A</ul>=0D=0A<p>I am having difficul=\nty uploading my resume. What should I do?</p>=0D=0A<P>Management applicants=\n: Save your resume in Rich Text Format (.rtf) format and try again.<br />Ho=\nurly applicants: Try cutting and pasting your resume into the text box and =\nuploading. All hourly applications are sent directly to the store you apply=\n for.</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">What are you l=\nooking for in qualified management candidates?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>We typically=\n look for a minimum of 2 years of full-service restaurant experience. But f=\nor us it goes beyond experience &mdash; we're looking for people who will t=\nhrive in our culture and embrace our&nbsp;<a href=3D\"http://www.cpk.com/faq=\ns/careers/#rock\">R.O.C.K.</a>&nbsp;philosophy and&nbsp;<a href=3D\"http://ww=\nw.cpk.com/faqs/careers/#fourkeys\">Four Keys to Success</a>. We want manager=\ns who are hospitality minded, motivated and can be themselves in a team env=\nironment. Of course, we also want them to have fun!</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A=\n\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">Does CPK offer a bonus program?</span>=0A\t\t=\n\t\t<p>Yes we do! Each level of management can potentially earn a bonus linke=\nd to key achievements in the restaurant. All bonuses are highly attainable =\nbased on meeting criteria and rewards for store performance.</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=\n=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">I have submitted my resume online =\nfor a posted management opportunity. When can I expect to hear back about s=\ncheduling an interview?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>You will be notified by email once =\nwe have received your submitted resume. We collect and screen applications =\nfor each of the positions posted. A recruiter will typically reach out to y=\nou to schedule a phone interview within two weeks of applying if there is i=\nnterest in moving forward to the next step of the process. If you have not =\nheard from us within three weeks of applying, we may have decided to pursue=\n another applicant. However, don't be discouraged if you don't hear back. P=\nlease feel free to reapply for other opportunities with us. We want to find=\n the best fit for everyone!</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span clas=\ns=3D\"q\">What is your management and hourly turnover?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>We hir=\ne the best and work hard to keep you! CPK has been benchmarked as having so=\nme of the lowest hourly and management turnover in the industry. We have be=\nen nationally recognized multiple times by People Report&trade; with their =\nBest People Practices Award for leading the industry in employee retention =\nand low turnover.</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t</ol>=0A\t</section>=0A</div>=0A<=\naside class=3D\"main\">=0A\t<div>=0A\t\t<hgroup>=0A\t\t\t<h1>FAQs</h1>=0A\t\t</hgroup>=\n=0A\t\t=0A        <nav>=0A            <ul>=0A\t            <li><a href=3D\"/faq=\ns/\" title=3D\"FAQs - General\" >General</a></li>=0A\t\t\t\t<li><a href=3D\"/faqs/m=\nenu/\" title=3D\"FAQs - Menu & Ordering\" >Menu & Ordering</a></li>=0A\t\t\t\t<li>=\n<a href=3D\"/faqs/gift-cards/\" title=3D\"FAQs - Gift Cards\"  >Gift Cards</a><=\n/li>=0A\t\t\t\t<li><a href=3D\"/faqs/catering/\" title=3D\"FAQs - Catering & Event=\ns\" >Catering & Events</a></li>=0A\t\t\t\t<li><a href=3D\"/faqs/careers/\" title=\n=3D\"FAQs - Careers\" class=3D\"on\">Careers</a></li>=0A\t\t\t\t<li><a href=3D\"http=\n://webhost.cpk.com/contactus/contactus.asp\" title=3D\"Contact Us\">Contact Us=\n</a></li>=0A            </ul>=0A        </nav>=0A\t</div>=0A</aside>=0A</div>=\n=0A=0A=0A=0A\t\t\t<footer>=0A\t\t\t\t<div>=0A\t\t\t\t\t<p>&copy; Copyright 2012 Califor=\nnia Pizza Kitchen, Inc. W=\nhere can I locate your nutritional information?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>We strive t=\no source premium ingredients and fresh vegetables and herbs are hand-cut in=\n our kitchens. We value your dietary needs, which is why we provide compreh=\nensive nutritional information on our website. Many of our menu items can b=\ne modified to fit your needs. We offer options like honey-wheat with whole =\ngrain pizza crust and multi-grain pasta. So explore our menu. One bite and =\nwe&rsquo;re sure you&rsquo;ll understand the delicious difference.</p>=0D=\n=0A<p>There are several documents you can download to help you navigate our=\n menu and guide you if you're interested in modifying your meal.</p>=0D=0A<=\nul>=0D=0A<li><a href=3D\"http://d32fh83nwkznvc.cloudfront.net/documents/nutr=\nition_facts.pdf\" target=3D\"_blank\">Nutritional Information</a></li>=0D=0A<l=\ni><a href=3D\"http://d32fh83nwkznvc.cloudfront.net/documents/vegetarian_and_=\nvegan_info.pdf\" target=3D\"_blank\">Vegetarian Information</a></li>=0D=0A<li>=\n<a href=3D\"http://d32fh83nwkznvc.cloudfront.net/documents/allergen_informat=\nion.pdf\" target=3D\"_blank\">Allergen Information</a></li>=0D=0A<li><a href=\n=3D\"http://d32fh83nwkznvc.cloudfront.net/documents/gluten_free_menu.pdf\" ta=\nrget=3D\"_blank\">Gluten-Free Menu</a></li>=0D=0A</ul>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t=\n<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">Can I order CPK for takeout or delivery?</span>=\n=0A\t\t\t\t<p>Absolutely! If you want your CPK to go, you can easily order onli=\nne or call your local CPK. We'll have your order ready to pick up when you =\narrive. Delivery is available at many of our locations &mdash; check with y=\nour local CPK to find out your options</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t=\n\t<span class=3D\"q\">Does CPK cater?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>Yes. We've designed a&nb=\nsp;<a href=3D\"http://www.cpk.com/catering/menu/\">Catering Menu</a>&nbsp;fea=\nturing a wide selection of signature CPK items. We offer options for partie=\ns large and small to fit within any budget. We even have a&nbsp;<a href=3D\"=\nhttp://www.cpk.com/catering/mobile-kitchen/\">mobile kitchen</a>&nbsp;that c=\nan bring everything we need to cater your party -- including the kitchen si=\nnk.</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">How do I contact=\n you about a recent experience I had as a guest at CPK?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>Ple=\nase tell us about your dining experience by clicking on any of the&nbsp;<a =\nhref=3D\"http://webhost.cpk.com/contactus/contactus.asp\">Contact Us</a>&nbsp=\n;links on the site or by calling 1-800-91-WE-CARE between 7:00 am and 12:00=\n am Pacific Time.</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">Do=\nes CPK have a kids menu?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>Our award-winning&nbsp;<a href=3D\"=\nhttp://d32fh83nwkznvc.cloudfront.net/documents/cpkids_menu.pdf\" target=3D\"_=\nblank\">CPKids Menu</a>&nbsp;is a popular favorite with children. Designed t=\no please kids 10 and under, your little ones are sure to find something the=\ny love.</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">How often do=\nes the CPK menu change?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>We introduce new menu items through=\nout the year, with two bigger launches in June and November. Gift cards cannot be reloaded at airport locatio=\nns, stadiums, universities, travel plazas and the Mirage Hotel in Las Vegas=\n. They are also not reloadable in Guam or international locations.</p>=0A\t\t=\n\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">Is it safe to give my credit=\n card information online?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>Keeping your information secure i=\ns a top priority for us. When you place your order through our website, you=\nr order information, including credit card number, is transmitted to our se=\ncure server. To validate the security of your order, please review the Trus=\ntwave validation seal when entering your payment information.</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=\n=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">In what dollar amounts are CPK Gif=\nt Cards available?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>CPK Gift Cards are available in whole do=\nllar denominations, in five-dollar increments, from $10 to $500.</p>=0A\t\t\t<=\n/li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">Does CPK charge a monthly serv=\nice fee for unused balances left on my CPK Gift Card?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>No, a=\n monthly service fee is not applied to our gift cards.</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=\n=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">Will you sell my information to other co=\nmpanies?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>We are as concerned about ensuring the privacy of =\nyour information as you are. For mor=\ne details, please refer to our&nbsp;<a href=3D\"http://www.cpk.com/privacy\">=\nprivacy policy</a>.</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">=\nI need a CPK Gift Card today and I do not live near a California Pizza Kitc=\nhen restaurant. Or, you can purchase our new eGift cards and it will be =\ninstantly emailed to you.</p>=0D=0A<p>We recommend shipping purchases over =\n$100 via FedEx. Bear in mind that Federal Express only ships to physical st=\nreet addresses and not P.O. Boxes, and that a signature is required for del=\nivery to a place of business. FedEx will make three attempts to deliver a p=\nackage.</p>=0D=0A<p>Delivery options and charges:</p>=0D=0A<ul>=0D=0A<li>Un=\nited States Postal Service (USPS) Standard Mail 5-7 business days (tracking=\n not included) $0.50</li>=0D=0A<li>Federal Express Ground Residential** 3-7=\n business days (tracking included) $6.50</li>=0D=0A<li>Federal Express 2 Da=\ny 2 days (tracking included) $11.25</li>=0D=0A<li>Federal Express Next Day =\nAir 1 day (tracking included) $20.00</li>=0D=0A</ul>=0D=0A<p>Orders receive=\nd after 11:00 a.m. (PST) Friday and prior to 11:00 a.m. (PST) on Monday wil=\nl be shipped on Monday. All orders placed after 11:00 a.m. (PT) will be pro=\ncessed the next business day. Time of delivery will depend upon the shippin=\ng option you choose.</p>=0D=0A<p>** Not available in Hawaii and Alaska</p>=\n=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">Can I place a CPK Gift =\nCard order for delivery to Hawaii or Alaska?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>Yes, we delive=\nr to Hawaii and Alaska via USPS Standard Mail and FedEx. Please note that U=\nSPS deliveries to Hawaii and Alaska take approximately 7-14 business days. =\nStandard Overnight and FedEx 2-Day are available for deliveries to Alaska. =\nHawaii offers FedEx 2-Day Shipping only. Also note that while shipping migh=\nt indicate overnight and 2-Day, there are regions in these areas that requi=\nre extra time for delivery.</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span clas=\ns=3D\"q\">Do you deliver on Saturday or Sunday?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>No, at this t=\nime we do not deliver on Saturday or Sunday. Box please choose USPS Standard Mail.</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t=\n\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">Can I place a CPK Gift Card order for delivery to APO =\naddresses?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>At this time we cannot deliver gift cards to APO=\n addresses.</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">Can I pl=\nace a CPK Gift Card order if I have an APO address? </span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>At thi=\ns time we cannot accept an online order if you have an APO billing address.=\n</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">I chose USPS Standa=\nrd Mail before and received my CPK Gift Card in 3 days, and another time it=\n took 7 days. Why?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>USPS Standard Mail service is reliant on=\n the distance the order has to travel, as well as mail volume. During peak =\nmail times, service may take longer than usual.</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<=\nli>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">Will I get confirmation of my CPK Gift Card ord=\ner? </span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>Yes, after your order is placed, you will be emailed a=\n confirmation that will include your order details.</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A=\n\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">How do I track my order?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>If=\n you chose Federal Express, your tracking number will be emailed to you whe=\nn your order is shipped. Tracking is not av=\nailable for USPS Mail orders.</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span cl=\nass=3D\"q\">What if I use USPS Standard Mail and my CPK Gift Card order takes=\n longer than expected or never shows up? </span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>Orders not delive=\nred in 14 business days will be replaced. The original CPK Gift Card will b=\ne deactivated and marked as stolen, and new cards will be issued. We recomm=\nend that you plan for USPS Standard Mail service to take 5-7 business days.=\n If your order does not arrive in that time, please call 1-800-91-WECARE or=\n email us at&nbsp;<a href=3D\"mailto:CustomerService@cpk.com\">CustomerServic=\ne@cpk.com</a>.</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">What =\nhappens if my CPK Gift Card does not work?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>CPK Gift Cards t=\nhat don't work properly can be loaded onto another card at any California P=\nizza Kitchen restaurant. You can also call our toll free number for further=\n assistance at 1-800-91-WECARE.</p>=0A\t\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span =\nclass=3D\"q\">Can I return a CPK Gift Card?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>Your CPK Gift Car=\nd cannot be redeemed for cash or credit, except as required by law.</p>=0A\t=\n\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">Who can I contact if I have=\n questions or problems with my CPK Gift Card order?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>You can=\n email us at&nbsp;<a href=3D\"mailto:CustomerService@cpk.com\">CustomerServic=\ne@cpk.com</a>&nbsp;or call our toll free number at 1-800-91-WECARE.</p>=0A\t=\n\t\t</li>=0A\t\t\t=0A\t\t\t<li>=0A\t\t\t\t<span class=3D\"q\">What happens if my CPK Gift=\n Card is lost or stolen?</span>=0A\t\t\t\t<p>Please treat your card like cash, =\nas CPK and CPK ASAP are not responsible for unauthorized use. This restaurant on wheels=\n includes ovens, saut&eacute; stations and coolers, which makes it easy to =\nbring our kitchen to your place. Recom=\nmended for events of 200 people or more.
